query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND n.gender in ('f') AND (n.name like '%f%' OR n.name like '%c%') AND (k.keyword like '%destined%' OR k.keyword like '%survival%' OR k.keyword like '%comedy%' OR k.keyword like '%redemption%' OR k.keyword like '%investigate%') AND it.info in ('LD picture format','sound mix','LD group genre','LD number','adaption','LD supplement','biographical movies','birth notes','LD label','LD release date','LD dynamic range','rating','LD analog left') AND (chn.name like '%Harley Quinn%' OR chn.name like '%Black Widow%') AND t.production_year > 2009 AND t.production_year < 2011 AND (pi.note like '%Eric Volkman%' OR pi.note like '%IW%') AND (rt.role like '%Don Mc Kay%' OR rt.role like '%Craig Good%' OR rt.role like '%PRW%' OR rt.role like '%Edward Bosco%' OR rt.role like '%Norman George%') AND cct1.kind not in ('complete+verified','crew','cast') AND (mc.note like '%Sweden%' OR mc.note like '%Japan%') AND mi.info in ('Kalmyk-Oirat','Mandarin','English','Croatian','Faroese','Greek','Norwegian','Greenlandic','Catalan','Galician','None','Indonesian','Dutch') AND (an.name like '%Y%' OR an.name like '%d%' OR an.name like '%i%') AND (cn.name like '%MGM Studios%') AND it3.info in ('color info','LD official retail price','LD additional information','LD contrast') AND cct2.kind in ('cast','complete+verified','crew')
